QuestData.Title: Wounded Wastewanderers
QuestData.Description:
Ahh, my friend, have you returned to render additional aid?
As you can see, we are still locked in battle with these creatures, with no end to their numbers in sight.
This is a war of attrition and we find ourselves at a clear disadvantage as injuries continue to mount.
Please, assist any of our wounded that you find within the ruins.
